    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "$47,900 - Mint-condition car being sold honestly as an exceptionally well-kept example. It presents beautifully inside and out, with a very clean exterior, a fresh and well-preserved interior, and the kind of overall appearance that stands out from typical used vehicles. Surfaces, trim, and materials show minimal wear, and it should feel tight, refined, and well cared for throughout. Buyers can expect a vehicle that needs no excuses, shows pride of ownership, and should make an excellent choice for someone looking for a top-condition used car.",
