    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical option for buyers seeking dependable basic transportation at a budget-conscious price. It shows its age cosmetically and is best suited for someone who values utility, simplicity, and strong value over perfection. A sensible choice for a commuter, backup vehicle, or project-minded owner.",
