      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with a bit of character? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great option for someone who wants a cheap runaround, a first project, or something to tinker with on weekends. It\u2019s being sold honestly and priced to reflect that, with plenty of potential left for the next owner. If you\u2019re handy, practical, or just want something budget-friendly, this could be a really worthwhile buy.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "\"Mechanic\u2019s special\" with solid project potential. Starts, runs, and offers a strong platform for someone who knows their way around maintenance and restoration. The powertrain feels fundamentally serviceable, and it\u2019s the kind of car that rewards a hands-on owner looking for an affordable entry point. Cosmetic wear and age-related needs are present, but that\u2019s reflected in the ask. Great candidate for a budget build, parts donor, or back-road beater with some wrench time.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap entry point. Honest poor-condition car with wear, but it still gets the job done. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with loads of personality, this car has the kind of seasoned character you just can\u2019t fake. It\u2019s the sort of ride that turns an ordinary errand into a story, with a presence that still feels bold and full of possibility. Perfect for someone who appreciates a hands-on project, a budget-friendly runabout, or a platform to make their own, it offers a chance to own something with spirit at a very accessible price. If you\u2019ve been looking for an inexpensive car with charm, potential, and plenty of life to give the right owner, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
